HEADWORD: Extrafoliaceous
<hw>Ex`tra*fo`li*a"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>extra-</ets> + <ets>foliaceous</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Away from the leaves, or inserted in a different place from them;
<as>as, <ex>extrafoliaceous</ex> prickles</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Loudon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
